# poker44-aquila — PUBLIC repo (deny-list). Published: the serving
# implementation (ensemble class, feature views, inference, miner entrypoint),
# the subnet framework, neurons/ and tests — everything a validator needs to
# verify the manifest's implementation hashes. Withheld: trained model
# weights/artifacts, the training/retrain/evaluation pipeline (know-how),
# README/docs prose, and wallet secrets.

